---
// 01 — Manifesto
---

<section class="section manifesto" id="manifesto">
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="section-header">
      <span class="mono">01 / Manifesto</span>
      <span class="eyebrow">Why we built this</span>
    </header>

    <p class="manifesto__lead display reveal">
      Great digital products are built with
      <em class="display-italic manifesto__accent">purpose</em>, strategy,
      experience, and genuinely
      <em class="display-italic manifesto__accent">great people</em>.
    </p>

    <div class="manifesto__body">
      <p class="reveal">
        FuseLab Digital is a boutique digital consultancy helping businesses
        harness technology to unlock new opportunities. We partner with
        organisations to solve complex challenges, optimise platforms, and
        create solutions that drive growth and efficiency.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal">
        Whether you are refining an existing product or exploring new digital
        frontiers, we bring the insight, experience, and hands-on approach to
        make it happen.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto__lead {
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 var(--s-8) 0;
    max-width: 22ch;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .manifesto__accent {
    color: var(--fuse-cyan);
  }

  .manifesto__body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--s-6);
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--bone-dim);
  }

  .manifesto__body p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .manifesto__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
